title: Abigail Cowen
itunes:title: Abigail Cowen
description:
Abigail Cowen [Chilling Adventures of Sabrina, Fate: The Winx Saga, Stranger Things, Redeeming Love] talks with Anna about her new movie Redeeming Love, figuring out priorities, how to recognize manipulative people, first loves and heartbreak, learning from mistakes, and a lot more.


Today’s Unqualified segment begins with a call from Wes who is bothered by his partner’s close relationship with an ex and wonders if he is overreacting. Next, Anna and Abigail talk with Alzita who doesn’t know how to tell her newly divorced best friend of 12 years that she is behaving selfishly.


Hosted on Acast. See acast.com/privacy for more information.
